Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:46.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:54.53,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用这对朱色翅膀掩去一切丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,000)}思念如附着的污渍般挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:11.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在这地球上生存着的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:19.03,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人窒息般地紧紧相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:25.23,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凝视着镜中的另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:31.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了隐藏自己的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:38.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去刺伤那些温柔善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:44.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:50.73,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}朱色的翅膀轻盈地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:57.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}烈火般的热吻一次次重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:02:09.23,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就用这最后一吻收敛起热情奔放的心
Dialogue: 2,0:22:24.84,0:22:31.33,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}太阳把热情的目光投向这边
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.54,0:22:36.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}真想好好享受这夏天 这阳光
Dialogue: 2,0:22:36.74,0:22:44.13,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天会发生什么令人激情澎湃的事吗
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.44,0:22:48.83,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}小小的不安点缀着这美妙的期盼
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.44,0:22:56.23,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)}夏天的回忆涌现在我脑际
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.13,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}晶亮的碎片注入天空大海充满世界
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.24,0:23:06.93,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,100)}低声私语请求你的拥抱
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.93,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}顽皮地挑逗
Dialogue: 2,0:23:09.94,0:23:14.93,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}不需要你做出暧昧的温柔
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.44,0:23:22.83,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,000)}那一瞬 我已经预感到一切
Dialogue: 2,0:23:22.84,0:23:26.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(000,300)}在这热情洋溢的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,HELLO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,新面孔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我爱纽·有司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又有奇怪的事情发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只是嘴上说说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说实在的 我现在更想去山上泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有谁会在那里等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,山 山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,说到夏天就是山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,山里有着浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有着新奇的东西 有着美好的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还有第三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还在说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真是不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在这样的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不能就两个人这么结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就要有第三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样擅自喜欢上我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,第三个人 第三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说要把光和明带去不同的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以还是听听她们的意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我去什么地方都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是和健在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,决定去山上野营
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,YEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,第六话 水边的伫立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,把叔叔一个人留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没有完成工作是他自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 今天也是可以休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要当司机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很无趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你昨晚不是答应了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只要准备酒 随便你们怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太记得昨晚的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里 这样不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都是要丧命的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还是和辽少爷同一部车好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不要老说些倒霉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我们好不容易同光和明一起出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和健...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,会掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样的风感觉很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧 光大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,让你们受惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是乱七八糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是玩得很开心的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 是....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,应该让她们更加的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这样看上去 这个就这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不错 很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是那样的性格就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快找第三个人 第三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 不由得...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快点下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害 滑滑的 滑滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到滑滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,滑滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看看 这里还有那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,滑滑的是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,被那样华丽的少女们所吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以倾听你所有的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,知道明在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,稍不注意 人就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 爱添麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那个 你的样子...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不能弄湿 是纪美说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,话是这样没错 确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥也是的 在那里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只是觉得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一碗 很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,健 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好大啊 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,健的专用料理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,请吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,专用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,健 难道你是想独占
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个幸运的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是健的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,光真是认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尽做些没意义的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,请吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,爱时常能成为凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,异常的爱 能忍受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但 与之相比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,像画中一样的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想进入画里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快点喝吧 鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是爱纽·有司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛 是嘛 所以就是鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爱纽·有司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,试胆会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 要说这里夏天的风俗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,果然就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,试胆会就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要说是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,甜甜的 软软的美好的事会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是怎么回事 但我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是游戏 轻松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,规则很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只要到那个大石头前面就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 请抽签配对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,1吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是1吗 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,抽签是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 反正我和谁一组都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我将来要和光大人一起保护地球环境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,管理树木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有着重要的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然被你说成是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,爱纽·有司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 不说些什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但要说什么 说什么光才会开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,学校 文艺 体育 自行车 将来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 完全找不到话题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是那么会说话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,天气好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是晴天真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:11:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,想一想的话 关于光我知道多少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说是从宇宙来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不是宇宙人 还说喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我该为光做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 怪物快出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 这样的话什么也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 沉默的话只会紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,以前说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在什么都没有的宇宙中彷徨着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,果然就是这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那里的确是什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,世界很远 只能看着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一瞬之后 就变得更远了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地面软软的接住了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和街道的地面完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,地面很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只是看着而弄不懂的事情 这里有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,触碰风和水还有很多的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就能明白很多的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,非常的有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么奇怪的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,以前踩着积水的池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一边回家感觉很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然忘了 但非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在说些什么完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不交给她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大家为什么都去试胆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能错过这样有趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐和健关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再多触碰些 就能更了解健
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就能变得更了解他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,光 我还没有心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,健 不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在跳动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看不清但一定出现了不错的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在这黑暗之中看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃 光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的有东西出现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 健
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要逃 快救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,健 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说话 抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爱纽·有司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,变态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,健 那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然会发生这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真是羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说他醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给大家带来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,澄慧阿姨不是常说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,酒不要喝太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤都被看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,发生这种事 我已经没有脸见人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这个锈豆机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不看事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:16:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,爱纽·有司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是开水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的设想终于成立了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,找到温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到能在这里泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,世间什么是幸福的事 真是不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对面酒 对面酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也让我喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我又没有什么容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,光大人也说些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不能任性 鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,作为惩罚就叫你鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是刚才的试胆会的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你和健在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 又没有人叫你重演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和健一样在跳动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对面好像发生了十分美妙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恨 憎恨这墙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,太小了 总该再做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩不要为这事斤斤计较
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊 健
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么 光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要我去那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还在下流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,光 如此的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候变得这么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,发着光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像是星星的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,光 对不起 是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了很过分的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不 健 不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那 究竟是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,心中有很多的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对健 大家 风 还有水和土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢的东西有很多的感受却...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很开心却...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是很开心的却...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么变得悲哀 寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,十分的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,节日结束就会莫名地感到悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但暑假还很长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还有许多开心和有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要感到悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我稍微考虑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只是如果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果就这样度过几天几个月几年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我和健到底会变得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:24:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,下回 这个丑与美的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,接吻的前奏曲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次遇见的可怕怪兽也会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,健 后面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.93,0:24:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,第七话 接吻的前奏曲
